
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Iceland 2026</title>
<style>
body{
    margin:0;
    font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;
    background:#0b0f14;
    color:white;
}
.hero{
    height:90vh;
    background-image:
    linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.45),rgba(0,0,0,.65)),
    url('https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Special:FilePath/Aurora_Borealis-Northern_Lights_Iceland.jpg?width=2400');
    background-size:cover;
    background-position:center;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    text-align:center;
    padding:40px;
}
.hero h1{
    font-size:64px;
    margin:0;
}
.hero p{
    font-size:22px;
    max-width:900px;
    line-height:1.5;
}
.container{
    width:92%;
    max-width:1400px;
    margin:auto;
}
.card{
    background:#121821;
    border-radius:24px;
    overflow:hidden;
    margin:50px 0;
    box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.4);
}
.card-gallery{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
    gap:22px;
    padding:22px 22px 0;
    background:#0b0f14;
}
.card-gallery img{
    width:100%;
    height:300px;
    object-fit:cover;
    display:block;
    border:1px solid #26364d;
    border-radius:18px;
    box-shadow:0 16px 34px rgba(0,0,0,.42);
}
.content{
    padding:35px;
}
h2{
    font-size:42px;
    margin-top:0;
}
h3{
    color:#77d8ff;
    font-size:28px;
}
p{
    font-size:20px;
    line-height:1.7;
}
.badge{
    display:inline-block;
    background:#1f2c3d;
    padding:8px 16px;
    border-radius:999px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}
.itinerary{
    margin:55px 0 30px;
    padding:34px;
    background:#121821;
    border:1px solid #233044;
    border-radius:24px;
}
.itinerary h2{
    margin-bottom:18px;
}
.trip-summary{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
    gap:14px;
    margin:26px 0 30px;
}
.summary-pill{
    background:#0e141d;
    border:1px solid #26364d;
    border-radius:16px;
    padding:16px;
}
.summary-pill strong{
    display:block;
    color:#77d8ff;
    font-size:18px;
    margin-bottom:6px;
}
.summary-pill span{
    color:#d9e8f5;
    font-size:16px;
}
.timeline-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);
    gap:22px;
}
.timeline-day{
    background:#0e141d;
    border:1px solid #26364d;
    border-radius:18px;
    padding:22px;
}
.timeline-day.critical{
    border-color:#77d8ff;
    box-shadow:0 0 0 1px rgba(119,216,255,.18),0 18px 36px rgba(0,0,0,.28);
}
.day-top{
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    gap:16px;
    align-items:flex-start;
    margin-bottom:16px;
}
.timeline-day h3{
    margin:0 0 12px;
    font-size:24px;
}
.route{
    color:#b9cadf;
    font-size:16px;
    margin:0;
}
.tag{
    flex:0 0 auto;
    background:#1f2c3d;
    border:1px solid #344962;
    border-radius:999px;
    color:#d9e8f5;
    font-size:14px;
    padding:8px 12px;
}
.event-list{
    display:grid;
    gap:10px;
}
.event{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:96px 1fr;
    gap:12px;
    align-items:start;
    padding:12px;
    background:#121a25;
    border-radius:14px;
}
.time{
    color:#77d8ff;
    font-weight:700;
    font-size:16px;
}
.event p{
    margin:0;
    font-size:18px;
    line-height:1.45;
}
.event small{
    display:block;
    color:#b9cadf;
    font-size:15px;
    margin-top:4px;
}
.quick-note{
    margin:24px 0 0;
    color:#b9cadf;
}
@media (max-width:900px){
    .trip-summary,
    .timeline-grid{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
    }
    .hero h1{
        font-size:44px;
    }
    .card-gallery{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
    }
    .card-gallery img{
        height:360px;
    }
    .day-top,
    .event{
        display:block;
    }
    .tag{
        display:inline-block;
        margin-top:8px;
    }
    .time{
        margin-bottom:6px;
    }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<section class="hero">
<div>
<h1>ICELAND 2026</h1>
<p>
7 días manejando entre volcanes, glaciares, playas negras y montañas imposibles.
No es un viaje normal. Es una expedición cinematográfica por Islandia.
</p>
</div>
</section>

<div class="container">

<section class="itinerary">
<h2>🌍 Roadbook Iceland 2026</h2>
<p>
Itinerario real de camper: horarios, rutas, paradas clave, supermercados, gasolina y campings.
</p>
<div class="trip-summary">
<div class="summary-pill"><strong>7 días</strong><span>KEF → Reykjavik → Golden Circle → Costa Sur → Este → KEF</span></div>
<div class="summary-pill"><strong>Modo</strong><span>Camper + campings estratégicos</span></div>
<div class="summary-pill"><strong>Regla</strong><span>⭐ = imperdible, pase lo que pase</span></div>
<div class="summary-pill"><strong>Clave</strong><span>Día 4 es el día crítico: glaciares + Jökulsárlón</span></div>
</div>

<div class="timeline-grid">
<article class="timeline-day">
<div class="day-top">
<div>
<h3>📅 Día 1 — Llegada + Reykjavik</h3>
<p class="route">🛣️ Ruta 41 → 49 → Reykjavik</p>
</div>
<span class="tag">Aterrizaje + setup</span>
</div>
<div class="event-list">
<div class="event"><span class="time">06:25</span><p>🛬 Llegada a KEF</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">07:30</span><p>Recoger camper <small>Ventana aproximada: 07:30–08:30</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">09:30</span><p>😴 Siesta clave <small>09:30–12:30 en zona Grindavík, cualquier parking tranquilo</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">13:30</span><p>🌆 Ruta hacia Reykjavik</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">14:30</span><p>🏙️ Ciudad <small>⭐ Hallgrímskirkja, Harpa, Sun Voyager. Hasta 17:30</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">17:30</span><p>🛒 Supermercado <small>Bónus barato. Alternativa: Krónan. Compra para 2–3 días</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">18:30</span><p>🏕️ Dormir <small>Reykjavík Eco Campsite</small></p></div>
</div>
</article>

<article class="timeline-day">
<div class="day-top">
<div>
<h3>📅 Día 2 — Golden Circle</h3>
<p class="route">🛣️ Ruta 36</p>
</div>
<span class="tag">Clásicos de Islandia</span>
</div>
<div class="event-list">
<div class="event"><span class="time">08:00</span><p>🌅 Salida</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">09:00</span><p>⭐ Þingvellir National Park <small>Hasta 10:30</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">11:30</span><p>📍 Geysir <small>Parada rápida</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">12:30</span><p>📍 Gullfoss Waterfall</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">13:30</span><p>🍔 Almuerzo <small>Geysir Visitor Center: rápido y fácil</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">15:30</span><p>📍 Kerið Crater</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">17:00</span><p>🛒 Reabastecer en Selfoss <small>IMPORTANTE: Bónus + gasolinera N1</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">18:30</span><p>🏕️ Dormir <small>Selfoss Campsite</small></p></div>
</div>
</article>

<article class="timeline-day">
<div class="day-top">
<div>
<h3>📅 Día 3 — Costa Sur</h3>
<p class="route">🛣️ Ruta 1, Ring Road</p>
</div>
<span class="tag">Cascadas + playa negra</span>
</div>
<div class="event-list">
<div class="event"><span class="time">08:00</span><p>🌅 Salida</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">09:00</span><p>📍 Seljalandsfoss + Gljúfrabúi</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">11:00</span><p>⭐ Skógafoss</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">12:30</span><p>🍔 Almuerzo <small>Skógar / food truck / gas station</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">13:30</span><p>📍 Dyrhólaey</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">14:30</span><p>⭐ Reynisfjara Beach</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">16:00</span><p>🛒 Reabastecer <small>Vík í Mýrdal: Krónan + N1</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">17:30</span><p>🏕️ Dormir <small>Vik Campsite</small></p></div>
</div>
</article>

<article class="timeline-day critical">
<div class="day-top">
<div>
<h3>📅 Día 4 — Glaciares</h3>
<p class="route">🛣️ Ruta 1</p>
</div>
<span class="tag">Día crítico</span>
</div>
<div class="event-list">
<div class="event"><span class="time">07:30</span><p>🌅 Salida</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">09:00</span><p>📍 Fjaðrárgljúfur <small>30 min máximo</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">10:30</span><p>📍 Skaftafell Visitor Center</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">11:00</span><p>⭐ Glacier Hike <small>11:00–14:00</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">14:30</span><p>🍔 Snack rápido / picnic</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">15:30</span><p>⭐ Jökulsárlón</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">16:30</span><p>📍 Diamond Beach</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">18:30</span><p>🏕️ Skaftafell Campground</p></div>
</div>
</article>

<article class="timeline-day">
<div class="day-top">
<div>
<h3>📅 Día 5 — Vestrahorn</h3>
<p class="route">🛣️ Ruta 1 Este</p>
</div>
<span class="tag">Tarde libre</span>
</div>
<div class="event-list">
<div class="event"><span class="time">08:30</span><p>🌅 Salida</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">10:30</span><p>⭐ Vestrahorn <small>Hasta 13:00. Incluye Stokksnes + Viking Village</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">13:30</span><p>🍔 Höfn <small>Comida / gasolina</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">14:30</span><p>🏕️ Camping zona Vestrahorn / Höfn</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">Tarde</span><p>Libre <small>Uno de los mejores momentos del viaje</small></p></div>
</div>
</article>

<article class="timeline-day">
<div class="day-top">
<div>
<h3>📅 Día 6 — Regreso</h3>
<p class="route">🛣️ Ruta 1, día largo de roadtrip</p>
</div>
<span class="tag">Con calma</span>
</div>
<div class="event-list">
<div class="event"><span class="time">08:00</span><p>🌅 Salida</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">10:00</span><p>☕ Skaftafell <small>Pausa</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">13:00</span><p>🍔 Vík <small>Comida + gasolina</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">15:00</span><p>📍 Dyrhólaey <small>Rápido, si quieren</small></p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">17:30</span><p>🏕️ Hvolsvöllur Campsite</p></div>
</div>
</article>

<article class="timeline-day">
<div class="day-top">
<div>
<h3>📅 Día 7 — Salida</h3>
<p class="route">🛣️ Ruta 1 → 41</p>
</div>
<span class="tag">Cierre</span>
</div>
<div class="event-list">
<div class="event"><span class="time">08:30</span><p>🌅 Salida hacia el aeropuerto</p></div>
<div class="event"><span class="time">10:30</span><p>📍 KEF</p></div>
</div>
</article>
</div>
<p class="quick-note">🧠 Lectura rápida: ⭐ = no negociable. Compras fuertes en Reykjavik, Selfoss y Vík. Día 4 manda el ritmo del viaje.</p>
</section>
 

